attr.title: Tiny Rally: Turbo Tour
attr.desc: Start your engines! It's time to race! Tiny Rally: Turbo Tour is a small arcade rally racing game made for #LOWREZJAM2020.
attr.inst: Download the game from Itch.io and extract all game files into the assets folder.
attr.inst_md: Download the game from [Itch.io](https://cosmiccrystal.itch.io/tiny-rally-turbo-tour) and extract all game files into the `assets` folder.
